Description: Fast Logfile Viewer for Analyzing Large Logfiles
 Chipmunk is a fast logfile viewer designed for analyzing large logfiles.
 It features super-fast search capabilities and is an invaluable tool for
 developers who need to analyze log data.
 .
 This package provides a user-friendly interface for searching and analyzing
 logfiles of any size.
